text: Læa mimi bap dı «kæ brrda phu thi meux phwk khea ma ha cea pheux hı cea cad hı phwk khea khi cea di klaw wa chan mi phb phahna thi ca hı phwk than khi bn man di phwk khea k phin hlang klab doythi naynta khxng phwk khea thwmthn pi dwy nata pheraa seiycı thi phwk khea mi phb sing thi phwk khea ca bricakh
